{"tid":181366,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】鯉魚門老店限量手做 芫茜蛋卷要食請等七日","createTime":"2017-03-31T14:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T08:24:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ac3d57080c1218bb7f6d65fff020a171070d14","tid":181366,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170331/56501541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170331%2F56501541&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=fb59dad9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170331%2F56501541&h=5acc00ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170331/56501541</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170330/large/1490869219_35d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170330%2Flarge%2F1490869219_35d2.jpg&h=24ae72ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本去年興起食好茜，任何食物也可以加一大堆芫茜同吃。其實這股芫茜熱，一早已傳來香港。在鯉魚門起家、有近50年歷史的蛋卷老店紹香園，多年來也堅持手做芫茜蛋卷，一賣就十多年。這款蛋卷起初不太受年輕人歡迎，只有老一輩的人才會幫襯，但最近因芫茜成為網上熱話，連帶芫茜蛋卷同樣人氣急升。「最難是多了一項工序，要加一塊芫茜在蛋卷面。要買新鮮貨，先浸洗，但不能太濕，以免影響蛋卷的香脆口感。」餅房總監朱先生說。不過芫茜味，未必人人頂得住，有人認為它像榴槤般，讓人愛恨分明。記者實試過後，認為芫茜味不算濃郁，對不好茜者是易入口的。不過想試也未必有得買，因為懂得做芫茜蛋卷的師傅不多，一星期可能只做到幾十盒，至今預訂也至少要等7至10日。<br />\n<br />\n紹香園<br />\n地址︰鯉魚門海傍道中46A<br />\n記者︰黃依情<br />\n攝影︰劉永發、潘志恆"},{"pid":"3e4b00a7e5d5b2d03cbf72450ff3b0e3fa1f43d8","tid":181366,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:40:13.000Z","msg":"送俾我都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11400234abaab1b173d7613e67644162f624411f","tid":181366,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"